        <h3>Source</h3>
                                    <div class="element-text">Li Han and Hsü Tzu-kuang.  Meng Ch&#039;iu: Famous Episodes from Chinese History and Legend. Transl. by Burton Watson. New York: Kodansha International, 1979, 23–4.</div>
